Twitter: SMS 2FA is only for Blue subscribers
text:
I long in to Twitter for the fist time in a while and this is the pop-up that I see:

You must remove text message two-factor authentication Only Twitter Blue subscribers can use the text message two-factor authentication method. It’ll just take a few minutes to remove it. You can still use the authentication app and security key methods.

To avoid losing access to Twitter, remove text message two-factor authentication by Mar 19, 2023.

https://imgur.com/a/PYHSnji
